\text{Area}(\bigtriangleup ADG)&=\frac{1}{2}(2+2\sqrt{2})(2+\sqrt{2})\\&=(1+\sqrt{2})(2+\sqrt{2})=\boxed{4+3\sqrt{2}}.
\end{align*} [asy]
